Rulings.Base: 1. If monsters are being treated as Zombies by "DNA Surgery" and you attempt to Summon a 2 copy of "Gravekeeper's Chief" while you already control one, it will be destroyed because this is not considered to be a card effect.\n2. If you control "Archfiend Zombie-Skull" and "Il Blud" and "Il Blud" is removed from the field, any monsters Summoned by the effect of "Il Blud" will not be destroyed.
